'''善牧堂'''（Church of the Good Shepherd）是一座[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]教堂，位于[[比佛利山_(加利福尼亚州)|比佛利山 (加利福尼亚州)]]北贝德福德路505号。

==历史==
堂区成立于1923年12月12日，1924年，由建筑师詹姆斯·唐纳利安设计，<ref name="history">{{Cite web |url=http://www.goodshepherdbh.org/a-city-on-a-hill/our-history/ |title=Official website, History |accessdate=2016-11-29 |archive-date=2018-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180102204124/http://www.goodshepherdbh.org/a-city-on-a-hill/our-history/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="owen">Thomas Owen, [http://www.sacredarchitecture.org/articles/los_angeles_and_the_mission_revival/ Los Angeles and the Mission Revival] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sacredarchitecture.org/articles/los_angeles_and_the_mission_revival/ |date=20170812060720 }}, ''Sacred Architecture'', Vol. 2, Summer 1999</ref><ref name="earlybh">Marc Wanamaker, ''Early Beverly Hills'', Arcadia Publishing, 2005, p. 118 [https://books.google.com/books?id=gwMyg0wEdDEC&pg=PA118]</ref>1925年2月1日祝圣<ref name="history"/> 它是比佛利山的最古老的教堂。<ref name="yahoolocal">{{Cite web |url=http://local.yahoo.com/info-20450039-good-shepherd-catholic-church-beverly-hills |title=Yahoo! Local |accessdate=2016-11-29 |archive-date=2017-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812103548/https://local.yahoo.com/info-20450039-good-shepherd-catholic-church-beverly-hills |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

